---
title: Chickpea Tikka Masala with Basmati, Yogurt, and Cilantro
description: This traditional Indian dish is famous for a good reason. Nutty chickpeas are stewed in a fragrant tomato stew flavored with ginger, garlic, spicy peppers, and curry. Fluffy basmati rice soaks up the delicious sauce while cool yogurt and cilantro add brightness.
